Among Bay Ridge's exceptional local restaurants... Leo’s Bay Ridge (Now on 85th & 3rd, it was the former 86th street Casa Calamari!!!) is the real deal!!! Everybody who has been there or sampled any of his creations knows about Leo's talent as not only a Chef at his landmark shop but as as a truly iconic Bay Ridge personality!!! Everybody L❤ves his food & raves about him as a Shopkeeper & vice-versa. Do people go crazy for the Leo Special or it's namesake?!? The answer is BOTH!!! The two  play off of one another... & neither would be AS awesome without the other!!!!!!!! Go for the great pizza & (wonderful, extensive...) Dinner menu & stay to have a few laughs with the ever-revolving cast of Brooklyn characters that flock to @Leo's BayRIdge!!!  (Added photos of just SOME of his awesome offerings... His FAMOUS Leo's special pie (His magical signature Vodka sauce & fresh mozzarella) the Leo's Riceball Special, Calamari in sauce, Chicken Marsala, Stuffed Mushrooms, baked clams & salmon oraganetta!!!)  Also: Don't forget to use them for your catering orders however big or small!!!!!!!!
